<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不喜欢学校的最后一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这意味着她会有两个月见不到朋友们了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道今天会做什么活动。” 伊坦对尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们往儿童中心走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。” 波比也加入他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是我在儿童中心的最后一天了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？” 尼娜惊讶地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个秋天，我会加入男生足球队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>放学后我需要训练。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再也不能玩儿四方格或者跳房子游戏了。” 他笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但尼娜觉得他很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把一大张纸铺在体育馆的地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要画一幅特别的壁画。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么特别呢？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不只是画画，你们还会在画里。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在画里？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要躺在纸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的搭档会用记号笔把你的身体描画下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，我们用旧布剪出衣服，粘在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还要用线做头发！” 雪莉老师笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你愿意作我的搭档吗？” 尼娜问莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一起吧。” 波比指着贾森和伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜脱下鞋子。她躺在纸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我描出来吧！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪开始沿着尼娜的腿和手臂描起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！好痒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪画好以后，尼娜看了看画。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。我有那么大吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轮到我了。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次，尼娜画莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，女生们开始选布料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们要做衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，这个很漂亮。” 尼娜拿起印着花的布料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要用这个做我的衬衫。” 莉琪拿起带圆点的布料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们把布放在画上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们开始测量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女生都选了蓝色的布料来做牛仔裤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们在选做头发的线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，给你。这个很像你的头发！” 伊坦拿起一团黄色的线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，这个给你，接着！” 波比把一团黑色的线扔给她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女生们用笔画脸，然后用线做头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在壁画里，孩子们都笑着手拉手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明年我不会来儿童中心了。” 贾森突然说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爸爸会在家工作。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也不来？” 尼娜简直不敢相信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天可真是让人伤心的一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会想念儿童中心的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，帮我爸爸做晚饭也会很有意思。” 贾森继续说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也会想你的。” 雪莉老师说，“女生们呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪耸耸肩。“我还不知道，但我想来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢儿童中心。” 尼娜大声说，“明年我还想回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴你能这么说！现在我们把壁画挂到墙上吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明年的儿童中心会完全不一样了。” 尼娜想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我会记住今年，今年是最棒的一年！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>